## 🧾 Account Deletion – MUHRA

**App Name:** MUHRA

MUHRA allows users to create an account inside the application.

### How to Delete Your Account

Account deletion is available **directly inside the MUHRA app**.

To delete your account:

1. Open the **MUHRASOFT** app By https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mohrasoft.muhra
2. Go to **Settings**
3. Select **Delete Account**
4. Confirm the deletion request

Once confirmed, the account deletion process will start immediately.

---

### Data Deletion Policy

When a user deletes their account: 
* ✅ All **personal user data** will be permanently deleted
* ✅ All **company-related data** associated with the account will be permanently deleted
* ✅ The deletion process is **irreversible**
* ✅ No data is retained after account deletion

All data is removed completely from our systems.




